"Marlynn":
"You're helping us again? Appreciate it.
So, do you have the vegetables?"
"Hmm, I don't think this will be enough. Could I bother you to get some more?"
"Yeah, these are nice and fresh. I should be able to put them to good use."
"We'll have our patients back on their feet in no time with food like this. I guess I'd better get to work."
"Are you alright? Don't you think you should take a break?"
"If you're hungry, I can make you something tasty."
"Sorry for all the work we've given you, but now I can finally make some good food."
"Well, I guess I'd better get to work."
